              <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/15/6701">15 U.S.C. 6701</external-xref> note</cato:entity-ref>)</cato:entity> is amended by
			 striking <quote>2017</quote> and inserting <quote>2024</quote>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection id="HCDB37BF2AF034A9895A18E0395F4D431">
        <enum>(c)</enum>
        <header>Termination
			 date</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">
          <cato:entity xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="law-citation">
            <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="Terrorism Risk Insurance Act of 2002/s:108/ss:a">Subsection (a) of
			 section 108 of the Terrorism Risk Insurance Act of 2002</cato:entity-ref> (<cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/15/6701/note">
              <external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/15/6701">15 U.S.C. 6701</external-xref> note</cato:entity-ref>)</cato:entity>
			 is amended by striking <quote>2014</quote> and inserting
			 <quote>2024</quote>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection commented="no" id="HBB7FA242847D4A8B9FA63301190F6BF5">
        <enum>(d)</enum>
        <header>Ongoing reports
			 regarding market conditions for terrorism risk insurance</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">
          <cato:entity xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="law-citation">
            <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="Terrorism Risk Insurance Act of 2002/s:108/ss:e/p:2">Paragraph (2) of section 108(e) of the
			 Terrorism Risk Insurance Act of 2002</cato:entity-ref> (<cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/15/6701/note">
